arguments.template:
<svg:g>
      <defs>
        <svg:g ngx-charts-svg-linear-gradient *ngIf="hasGradient"
          orientation="vertical"
          ng-attr-[name]="{{gradientId}}"
          ng-attr-[stops]="{{gradientStops}}"
        />
      </defs>
      <svg:g ngx-charts-area
        class="line-highlight"
        ng-attr-[data]="{{data}}"
        ng-attr-[path]="{{areaPath}}"
        ng-attr-[fill]="{{hasGradient ? gradientUrl : colors.getColor(data.name)}}"
        ng-attr-[opacity]="{{0.25}}"
        ng-attr-[startOpacity]="{{0}}"
        ng-attr-[gradient]="{{true}}"
        ng-attr-[stops]="{{areaGradientStops}}"
        ng-attr-[class.active]="{{isActive(data)}}"
        ng-attr-[class.inactive]="{{isInactive(data)}}"
        ng-attr-[animations]="{{animations}}"
      />
      <svg:g ngx-charts-line
        class="line-series"
        ng-attr-[data]="{{data}}"
        ng-attr-[path]="{{path}}"
        ng-attr-[stroke]="{{stroke}}"
        ng-attr-[animations]="{{animations}}"
        ng-attr-[class.active]="{{isActive(data)}}"
        ng-attr-[class.inactive]="{{isInactive(data)}}"
      />
     <svg:g ngx-charts-area
        *ngIf="hasRange"
        class="line-series-range"
        ng-attr-[data]="{{data}}"
        ng-attr-[path]="{{outerPath}}"
        ng-attr-[fill]="{{hasGradient ? gradientUrl : colors.getColor(data.name)}}"
        ng-attr-[class.active]="{{isActive(data)}}"
        ng-attr-[class.inactive]="{{isInactive(data)}}"
        ng-attr-[opacity]="{{rangeFillOpacity}}"
        ng-attr-[animations]="{{animations}}"
      />
    </svg:g>
